<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>로또 번호 추천</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/pick.css?v=<%= Date.now() %>">
</head>
<body>
    <!-- 헤더 -->
    <header class="header">
        <div class="header-top">
            <a href="/dashboard" class="btn-nav" title="대시보드로 이동">&#9664; 이전</a>
            <h1 class="drw-title">--- 회차 로또 번호 추천</h1>
        </div>
        <p class="header-sub">원하는 추천 방식을 선택하고 결과를 확인하세요.</p>
    </header>

    <!-- 1행: 전략 방식 선택 -->
    <section class="section-panel">
        <h1 class="section-title"><span class="step-tag">STEP 1</span> <b>| 추천 방식을 선택하세요.</b></h1>
        <div class="progress-bar">
            <div class="progress-track">
                <div class="progress-fill" id="progress-fill"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="progress-dot active" data-step="1"></div>
            <div class="progress-dot" data-step="2"></div>
            <div class="progress-dot" data-step="3"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="strategy-grid">
            <button class="btn-strategy active" data-strategy="random">🎲 Random</button>
            <button class="btn-strategy" data-strategy="hotCold">🔥 HotCold</button>
            <button class="btn-strategy" data-strategy="evenOdd">🔄 EvenOdd</button>
            <button class="btn-strategy" data-strategy="frequency">📊 Frequency</button>
            <button class="btn-strategy" data-strategy="sumRange">➕ SumRange</button>
            <button class="btn-strategy" data-strategy="all">🧩 All</button>
        </div>
        <div class="desc-grid">
            <p class="strategy-desc active" data-strategy="random"><span class="desc-title">RANDOM 추천 방식</span> 입니다.<br>특정 패턴 없이 1~45 사이에서 완전 무작위로 번호를 생성합니다.</p>
            <p class="strategy-desc" data-strategy="hotCold"><span class="desc-title">HOTCOLD 추천 방식</span> 입니다.<br>최근 출현 빈도가 높은 번호와 낮은 번호를 조합합니다.</p>
            <p class="strategy-desc" data-strategy="evenOdd"><span class="desc-title">EVENODD 추천 방식</span> 입니다.<br>짝수와 홀수 비율을 균형 있게 맞춰 생성합니다.</p>
            <p class="strategy-desc" data-strategy="frequency"><span class="desc-title">FREQUENCY 추천 방식</span> 입니다.<br>과거 데이터 기반 출현 빈도를 반영하여 번호를 추천합니다.</p>
            <p class="strategy-desc" data-strategy="sumRange"><span class="desc-title">SUMRANGE 추천 방식</span> 입니다.<br>번호 합계가 평균 범위에 들어오도록 조정합니다.</p>
            <p class="strategy-desc" data-strategy="all"><span class="desc-title">ALL 추천 방식</span> 입니다.<br>각 전략을 한 번씩 적용하여 전략별 결과를 모두 제공합니다.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 2행: 필수 포함 & 제거 및 카운트  -->
    <section class="section-panel">
        <h1 class="section-title"><span class="step-tag">STEP 2</span> <b>| 세부 옵션을 설정하세요.</b></h1>
        <div class="progress-bar">
            <div class="progress-track">
                <div class="progress-fill" style="width: 50%"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="progress-dot done" data-step="1"></div>
            <div class="progress-dot active" data-step="2"></div>
            <div class="progress-dot" data-step="3"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="step2-layout">
            <!-- 왼쪽: 위/아래 -->
            <div class="step2-left">
                <div class="step2-box">
                    <h3 class="step2-box-title">
                        필수 포함 번호
                        <span class="tooltip-wrap">
                            <button type="button" class="btn-tooltip">?</button>
                            <span class="tooltip-bubble">1 ~ 45 범위에서 최대 <b>6개</b>까지 지정할 수 있습니다.</span>
                        </span>
                    </h3>
                    <div class="fixed-input-row" id="fixed-numbers">
                        <input type="text" class="input-fixed" name="fixed[]" inputmode="numeric" maxlength="2" placeholder="-">
                        <input type="text" class="input-fixed" name="fixed[]" inputmode="numeric" maxlength="2" placeholder="-">
                        <input type="text" class="input-fixed" name="fixed[]" inputmode="numeric" maxlength="2" placeholder="-">
                        <input type="text" class="input-fixed" name="fixed[]" inputmode="numeric" maxlength="2" placeholder="-">
                        <input type="text" class="input-fixed" name="fixed[]" inputmode="numeric" maxlength="2" placeholder="-">
                        <input type="text" class="input-fixed" name="fixed[]" inputmode="numeric" maxlength="2" placeholder="-">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="step2-box">
                    <h3 class="step2-box-title">
                        필수 제외 번호
                        <span class="tooltip-wrap">
                            <button type="button" class="btn-tooltip">?</button>
                            <span class="tooltip-bubble">1 ~ 45 범위에서 최대 <b>6개</b>까지 지정할 수 있습니다.</span>
                        </span>
                    </h3>
                    <div class="exclude-input-row" id="exclude-numbers">
                        <input type="text" class="input-exclude" name="exclude[]" inputmode="numeric" maxlength="2" placeholder="-">
                        <input type="text" class="input-exclude" name="exclude[]" inputmode="numeric" maxlength="2" placeholder="-">
                        <input type="text" class="input-exclude" name="exclude[]" inputmode="numeric" maxlength="2" placeholder="-">
                        <input type="text" class="input-exclude" name="exclude[]" inputmode="numeric" maxlength="2" placeholder="-">
                        <input type="text" class="input-exclude" name="exclude[]" inputmode="numeric" maxlength="2" placeholder="-">
                        <input type="text" class="input-exclude" name="exclude[]" inputmode="numeric" maxlength="2" placeholder="-">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- 오른쪽 -->
            <div class="step2-right">
                <div class="step2-box count-box">
                    <h3>생성 개수</h3>
                    <div class="counter-wrap">
                        <button type="button" class="btn-counter" id="btn-minus">−</button>
                        <span class="counter-value" id="counter-value">1</span>
                        <button type="button" class="btn-counter" id="btn-plus">+</button>
                    </div>
                    <p class="counter-hint" id="counter-hint">최대 10세트</p>
                </div>
                <button type="button" class="btn-recommend" id="btn-recommend">번호 추천받기</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 3행: 추천 결과물  -->
    <section class="section-panel" id="section-result">
       <h1 class="section-title"><span class="step-tag">STEP 3</span> <b>| 추천 결과를 확인하세요.</b></h1>
        <div class="progress-bar">
            <div class="progress-track">
                <div class="progress-fill" style="width: 100%"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="progress-dot done" data-step="1"></div>
            <div class="progress-dot done" data-step="2"></div>
            <div class="progress-dot active" data-step="3"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="result-empty" id="result-empty">
            <p>아직 추천 결과가 없습니다.</p>
            <p>위에서 옵션을 설정하고 <b>번호 추천받기</b>를 눌러주세요.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="result-list" id="result-list"></div>
    </section>

    <script src="/js/pick.js?v=<%= Date.now() %>"></script>
</body>
</html>